* http://id3.org/id3v2.3.0
    * [0]     = 'I'
    * [1]     = 'D'
    * [2]     = '3'
    * [3,4]   = {Version}
    * [5]     = {Flags}
    * [6-9]   = {ID3 Size}
    *
    * An ID3v2 tag can be detected with the following pattern:
    *  $49 44 33 yy yy xx zz zz zz zz
    * Where yy is less than $FF, xx is the 'flags' byte and zz is less than $80
